Package: PBAT
Title: Plant Breeding Analytical Tools (Shiny App)
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Krishnan P", "Abhijith", email = "abhijithkpgen@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8641-026X"))
    )
Description: An interactive Shiny application for plant breeding analyses, including mating-design analytics (diallel, line-by-tester, partial diallel), ANOVA summaries, GCA/SCA effects, BLUE/BLUP utilities, PCA and plotting, and exportable reports. Designed for non-programmers with a point-and-click interface.
